snippet.title: Sensible World of Soccer gameplay (PC Game, 1994)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Sensible World of Soccer (aka SWOS), Dos PC game produced by Sensible Software in 1994 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/sensible-world-of-soccer/640/
Playing Champions League as Juventus. Passing first session and then defeated at quarter of final by Blackburn Rovers. Real Madrid will win the cup finally.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Football Glory - https://youtu.be/hEvsng-OetI
Sensible World of Soccer 96/97 - https://youtu.be/tNFOyF9bVt4
Kick Off 3: European Challenge - https://youtu.be/1LJD3vX1Ld8
